Here you find the dsdt source file for the Gigabyte GA-EP45-DS4 Motherboard

- HPET Fix
- RTC Fix
- AppleRTC Fix
- CMOS reset fix
- Add LAN devices to fix Time Machine and UUID bugs
- Add section to use Vanilla High Definition Audio kext in Leopard 10.5.7
- Activation of Power Button
- Shutdown Fix
- EHCI USB Ports sleeping fix

Other infos:
- Don't try to force pciroot to be 0 because it can cause some problems like the impossible to use an Atheros based PCI WLAN board with Gigabyte EP45 motherboards
